          "$\\lim_{x\\to +\\infty} \\frac{e^x}{x^n} = +\\infty$, $\\lim_{x\\to +\\infty} \\frac{\\ln x}{x^n} = 0$",
          "$\\lim_{x\\to 0^+} x^n \\ln x = 0$"
        ]
      },
      {
        "title": "Fonction arctangente",
        "content": [
          "$\\arctan : \\mathbb{R} \\to ]-\\pi/2, \\pi/2[$ est la bijection réciproque de $\\tan$.",
          "$\\arctan'(x) = \\frac{1}{1+x^2}$",
          "$\\forall x > 0 : \\arctan x + \\arctan(1/x) = \\pi/2$"
